OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775473375
OL,3,CDurham Cricket shuts stadium to
OL,4,Cspectators after stadium damage in
OL,5,CStorm Dave
OL,7,FAs a result game play at the ground in
OL,8,FChester-le-Street will not start when
OL,9,Fexpected. Today (5 April) was expected
OL,10,Fto be day three of Durham's County
OL,11,FChampionship Division Two clash
OL,12,Fagainst Kent
OL,14,FThe club are encouraging spectators
OL,15,Fnot to travel to the ground and wait
OL,16,Ffor further updates.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
