OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775473375
OL,3,CDurham Cricket shuts stadium to
OL,4,Cspectators after stadium damage in
OL,5,CStorm Dave
OL,7,F"The Club have been in discussions
OL,8,Fwith the match officials and venue
OL,9,Fstaff this morning and following the
OL,10,Fimpact on the pitch and structures
OL,11,Fwithin the ground ` it is confirmed
OL,12,Fthat play will not commence on time,
OL,13,Fand a further update will be provided
OL,14,Fin due course.
OL,16,F"Until further assessment have taken
OL,17,Fplace our ground safety team have
OL,18,Fdecided it is unsafe to allow
OL,19,Fspectators into the venue.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
