OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1775473375
OL,3,CDurham Cricket shuts stadium to
OL,4,Cspectators after stadium damage in
OL,5,CStorm Dave
OL,7,F"The ground will remain closed to
OL,8,Fmembers and spectators until further
OL,9,Fnotice. Please do not travel to Banks
OL,10,FHomes Riverside for today's play."
OL,12,FIt added: "As the safety of all
OL,13,Fplayers, staff and spectators is the
OL,14,FClub's number one priority spectators
OL,15,Fare requested not to travel to the
OL,16,Fground and the Club will provide an
OL,17,Fupdate in due course.
OL,19,F"The safety of all in attendance is
OL,20,Four number one priority in any
OL,21,Fdecisions we make.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
